Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.69,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ここは僕らの戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:50.50,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}少し先の理想すら追えない{\fsp1}…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.91,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉 一つのみ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.24,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 そっと閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:02.14,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}今はただ 振動に応えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.19,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}心の瞳(め)で Lock-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.94,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}君が叫ぶ Push up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.65,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}この痛みと熱さが答だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.96,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-キミハマダ戦エル-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.56,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}幻聴か?否か?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:24.28,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}<回路=意識>(カイロ)を意思で導け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:29.54,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}決してのみ込まれるな 無限の谷へと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:35.30,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}目の前の不条理を壊せ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Can you break up endless war?
Comment: 1,0:01:31.81,0:01:34.42,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}You just call up circuit zone!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.26,0:01:42.92,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}"思緒"擾亂心中平靜
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.69,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這裡是我們的戰場
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.76,0:01:50.50,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}連眼前的理想都無法追尋{\fsp1}…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.91,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言語 嚥回腹中
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.24,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 鎖在心裡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.36,0:02:02.14,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}如今只要 回應這振動就好
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.19,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}睜開心眼 Lock-on!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.94,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}你在呼喊 Push up!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.65,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這痛楚和灼熱便是答案!!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.96,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-你還能繼續戰鬥-
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.56,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這是幻聽嗎?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.56,0:02:24.28,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}意識 用意志來引導
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.38,0:02:29.54,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}謹記不要被吞入 那不見底的深淵
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.54,0:02:35.30,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}擊潰眼前的荒唐不經!
Comment: 1,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.88,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Can you break up endless war?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:13.23,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見つめ合う  心  ひらいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:19.18,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}強がりと弱さのループ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:25.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ねえ少しは  慣れたはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:35.95,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉にしても全てのことは  わからないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:40.46,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}それだけは覚えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:43.67,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}こんなものじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.01,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}自分に気付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:54.21,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}勇気に乗せたなら  世界は変わっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:01.98,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}独りじゃ知らなかった  あのTELEPATHY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:08.45,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}導く  後ろ姿  とても眩しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:15.48,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}だから私は  目をそらさず君を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:22.40,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}届くと  信じている
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.07,0:22:13.23,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}對視凝望  將心扉敞開
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.63,0:22:19.18,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}逞強與軟弱的循環
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.52,0:22:25.88,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}吶  是不是  略微習慣了些
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.30,0:22:35.95,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}即便用語言闡述  也不是一切事情  都能清晰明瞭
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.41,0:22:40.46,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我只記住了這個道理
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.60,0:22:43.67,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}並不是這樣
